description: Bartleby Montclair of Dresdin, and his lover, Sonic the hedgehog, enter the great corn maze competition at Glen Acre's, in hopes of winning a years worth of juicy pumpkin pies. Meanwhile Uncle Chuck enters in hopes of getting spanked by one of the hot pumpkin girls.
